languages.text: "По счастью, пострадало немного комплексов — наша непримиримая борьба отодвинула границы пораженного сектора. Важные производства уцелели".
"Fortunately, not too many facilities were damaged — our irreconcilable struggle has moved the borders of the affected sector. The important production lines have survived."

languages.text: “幸运的是，遭到破坏的设施并不太多。这场无法和解的斗争转移到了受灾地区的边界，重要的生产线完好无损。”
languages.original_text: "Fortunately, not too many facilities were damaged — our irreconcilable struggle has moved the borders of the affected sector. The important production lines have survived."

traits.locale_text: “幸运的是，遭到破坏的设施并不太多。这场无法和解的斗争转移到了受灾地区的边界，重要的生产线完好无损。”

languages.text: «Afortunadamente, no han resultado dañadas demasiadas instalaciones: nuestra lucha sin cuartel ha desplazado las fronteras del sector afectado. Las líneas de producción importantes han sobrevivido».
languages.original_text: "Fortunately, not too many facilities were damaged — our irreconcilable struggle has moved the borders of the affected sector. The important production lines have survived."

languages.text: 「幸いなことに、被害が出た施設はそれほど多くはなかった...我々の妥協できない奮闘により、被害を受けたセクターの境界を動かしました。大切な製造ラインはまだ稼働しています」
languages.original_text: "Fortunately, not too many facilities were damaged — our irreconcilable struggle has moved the borders of the affected sector. The important production lines have survived."

languages.text: « Par chance, peu d'installations ont été endommagées, car notre lutte incessante a déplacé les frontières du secteur touché. Les chaînes de production les plus importantes ont survécu. »
languages.original_text: "Fortunately, not too many facilities were damaged — our irreconcilable struggle has moved the borders of the affected sector. The important production lines have survived."

languages.text: "Glücklicherweise wurden nicht zu viele Einrichtungen beschädigt — unser unerbittlicher Kampf hat die Grenzen des betroffenen Sektors verschoben. Die wichtigen Produktionsstätten haben überlebt."

languages.text: "Neyse ki çok fazla tesis hasar görmemiş. Uzlaşma yolumuz olmayan mücadelemiz, etkilenen sektörün sınırlarına taşınmış. Önemli üretim hatları sağlam kalmış."
languages.original_text: "Fortunately, not too many facilities were damaged — our irreconcilable struggle has moved the borders of the affected sector. The important production lines have survived."
